        Some contractor positions may be eligible for employment at the end of the contractual assignment, but are not guaranteed. Please discuss career opportunities with your manager. The College Board is committed to equity in education and to diversity in the workplace. We are an equal opportunity employer.
    </p>
    <p class="vspace">
